title: Untying The Knot S01E02 Passport For Divorce WS DSR x264-[NY2] m
description:
Ep 2: Passport For Divorce
After 13 years, Jennifer and Golan called Vikki to help end their marriage and divide their assets.image
After 13 years, Jennifer and Golan haven't been very lucky in love and have decided to call Vikki to help end their marriage and divide their assets. These two are stuck in a real crisis and are clinging to a historically significant antique passport, a diamond necklace, a painting by a famous artist, and five income-producing properties.
